com.sun.j3d.utils.behaviors.mouse.MouseBehaviorCallback
public class PickZoomBehavior
extends PickMouseBehavior
implements com.sun.j3d.utils.behaviors.mouse.MouseBehaviorCallback

A mouse behavior that allows user to pick and zoom scene graph objects. Common usage: 1. Create your scene graph. 2. Create this behavior with the root and canvas. See PickRotateBehavior for more details.
